  "title": "Part-Time Sales Associate #SeniorsWelcome",
  "description": "<p><em>Stefani Parfumerie is looking for Part-Time Retail Assistant!</em><br /><br /><em>Join us if you have passion in Home Fragrances & Customer Service or love interacting with customers!</em></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Interact with customers to sell products and provide customer service</li><li>Product knowledge and recommendations based on customer preferences and needs</li><li>Weekly stock replenishment/stock take</li><li>Maintain housekeeping standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to commit 2-3 weekdays & 1 weekend</li><li>Service-oriented and team player</li><li>Prior experience in Retail and / or service Industry will be an added advantage</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Shift : Retail Hours</li><li>Location : Town Area</li><li>Remuneration : $13/hr + <em><strong>**commission**</strong></em></li><li>Attire : All Black smart casual outfits</li></ul><p>To know more about our products, please visit us at: https://stefaniparfumerie.com/</p><p><br />Interested candidate, click APPLY!</p>",
